'''Murder 4''' is a cross-compatible player-versus-player horror [[Special:MyLanguage/:Category:Game worlds|game world]], created by ''Jar'' in 2020. Up to twenty-four players can play at a time, but a minimum of three players must be present to begin. There are three possible roles to play as: The '''Detective''', '''Bystander(s)''', and '''Murderer'''. There are clues, photographs, weapons, and hazards that players will encounter. The objective of the Murderer is to eliminate every player in the mansion. The objective of the Detective is to find out and eliminate the murderer, and the Bystanders is to work together to identify and neutralize the Murderer.